name: Digital chains
description: The individual who produces content in digital media and presents the content he produces to his followers, starts to prepare content after a while in line with the demands and likes of his followers or the direction of the sponsoring institutions/brands. The fact that individuals present the information they produce in digital media to the appreciation of other selves puts them in the other class. Individuals who produce content, who are the modern slaves of the new era, are included in the respected other class.
